Configure extensions : press F1 search open settings(json) - settings.json

material icon theme : icon next to html, Css and ...

press F1 and search Toggle screencast mode to see what you type on keyboard

Html preview : ctrl + k then press V */ it is no longer maintained */

Color highlight : maked color style highlight

codesnap : take screen shot from your code press F1 + select code snap

svg preview : perview of svg images

glassit-VSC : to make the background galssy : ctrl + Alt + Z/C

project manager : save projects and easy access : press F1 - save project

Intellisense for Css class names : easy access to Css values in html

prettier code-formatter : press shift + Alt + F to normalize and fix your code

bracket pair colorizer : paint the start and end brackets ( best for  lots of if else  brackets )

minify : to mix and compress the project codes and reduce the size of codes
press F1 - minify : it will create a index.min.html file

live Sass compiler : convert SCss codes to Css

TODO tree : if you forget you can use this add comment // TODO or //FIXME

Better comments : to colorify the comments in different colors //! - ? - ! and ..

Document this : to comment more than one line press ctrl + D two times 
 
